<p>
  Sorry, it looks like I broke something on my website. Please
  <a href="/contact/">send me</a> the URL in your address bar and tell me where you found it.
</p>

<a class="button" href="/">
  &larr; Take me home
</a>

<p>
  If you're feeling brave, you can try to find it yourself:
</p>

<details>
  <summary>Show all pages...</summary>
  <dl>
  {%- assign sortedPosts = collections.all | sortByLocale: "url" -%}
  {% for post in sortedPosts %}
  {% unless post.data.draft %}
    <dt>{{ post.data.title | fallback: post.url | escape }}</dt>
    <dd>
      <a href="{{ post.url | escape }}">{{ post.url | escape }}</a>
    </dd>
  {% endunless %}
  {%- endfor -%}
  </dl>
</details>
